{"product_id":"cr7-attar-roll-on-6ml-al-saalim-perfumers-alcohol-free","title":"CR7 Attar (Roll-On 6ml) | Al-Saalim Perfumers | Alcohol-Free","description":"\u003cp\u003e Feel the fresh, energetic, and modern fragrance of CR7 Attar by Al-Saalim Perfumers.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis attar is perfect for those who prefer a sporty, stylish, and confident scent.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCR7 offers a fresh and vibrant aroma, making it ideal for daily wear, gym sessions, office use, and casual outings.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIts alcohol-free formula is skin-friendly and keeps the fragrance clean and long-lasting.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eKey Features\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFragrance Type: Fresh, Sporty \u0026amp; Modern\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eQuantity: 6 ml Roll-On\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAlcohol-Free\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eLong-lasting and refreshing fragrance\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePremium glass roll-on bottle\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSuitable for men\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWhy Choose CR7 Attar\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eYouthful and energetic fragrance\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePerfect for daily use\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFresh, headache-free scent\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eStylish packaging, also a great gifting option\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHow to Use\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eApply a small amount on your neck, wrists, or pulse points and enjoy an all-day fresh and confident fragrance.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"AL-SAALIM PERFUMES","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50472866283767,"sku":null,"price":179.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0923\/0755\/4551\/files\/97B70408-4111-45F3-98A8-1D3734864D28.png?v=1777870290","url":"https:\/\/alsaalimperfume.shop\/products\/cr7-attar-roll-on-6ml-al-saalim-perfumers-alcohol-free","provider":"AL-SAALIM PERFUMES","version":"1.0","type":"link"}